author: mwomack
msg: Defined new method in Plugin, isEquivalent().  Used by PluginRegistry to see if 2 plugins are equivalent.  Using this instead of overriding the equals() method which has too many implications to deal with normally.

author: mwomack
msg: Changed equals() method to new Plugin method isEquivalent.  This method is used by PluginRegistry when a new plugin is being started.  If an equivalent plugin is already running, it is left running and the new plugin is not started.
